{
  "chapter": 93,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙伤愈后在府中接待赵雅来访。赵雅以关心为名探听他与赵穆的关系，项少龙巧妙周旋。赵雅透露乐乘之死赵穆嫌疑最大，但因缺乏真凭实据，孝成王不敢轻举妄动。项少龙从赵雅口中得知乐乘是两面蛇，在赵穆与孝成王间左右逢源，故双方均疑对方所为，田单、李园亦被无辜牵连。赵雅临别向项少龙暗示情意，称已找到取代项少龙的人。回到内宅，善柔展示她绘制的邯郸城防图，随后二人在房中经历一番暧昧纠缠。善柔坦承自己一向不服男尊女卑，项少龙尊重她的想法，最终二人约定掩耳盗铃般共赴空房。本章以\"掩耳盗铃\"为题，既指善柔自欺欺人的行径，也暗喻各势力在邯郸的尔虞我诈。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "可以起来走动了吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "再不爬起来，闷也要闷出病来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你的身子比龙阳君好多了。到现在他仍赖在榻上，看来没有十天、八天，休想复原过来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "韩闯来找你干嘛？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "哪会有什么好事？这好色的家伙看上了鄙人那对孪生姊妹花，想借去风流快活，给我回绝。哼！他不高兴又怎么样，我董某人最不喜欢这调调儿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你和赵穆究竟是什么关系？为何他对你特别照顾？今早又匆匆前来找你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你问我，我去问谁？本人亦无须向任何人解释为何某某人对我特别好，又或对我特别不好！我董匡管他的娘。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人家很爱看你生气的样子，像个撒野的孩子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "没人叫你要黏着我嘛！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你的旧情人闯进城来行凶，你还像很有闲情逸致的样子，算他娘的什么一回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这片叶子比你香多了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你没有在听我说话吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你的嗓子既特别又充满性格，人家想不听都不行。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董马痴原来也像其他人那样，以为是项少龙到来杀人放火。不过不知者无罪，你既然不明白邯郸的情况，自然像盲人般只懂瞎猜了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "难道不是项少龙吗？那谁与乐乘有如此深仇大恨，非置他于死地不可？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "杀人定要有仇恨吗？想知道是谁有可能杀死乐乘的话，得先告诉我赵穆今早来找你说了什么？唉！你难道不知人家关心你吗？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你真的对我那么好吗？我看是怕我有什么三长两短，截不住项少龙吧！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "算是两样都有好了，够坦白吧！快告诉我。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你总是独断独行，不理别人，不知现在邯郸危机四伏，一不小心，就是诛家灭族的大祸，赵雅也保你不住，还要使性子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "他根本没有什么机密，只是来向我询问楚国的情况。我看巨鹿侯颇有点心事，当时我还猜他是给你那神出鬼没的旧情人吓怕了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这事本不应告诉你，但人家怕你受赵穆牵连，故逼得要说出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "乐乘之死，赵穆的嫌疑最大。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你知道这点就够了，莫再追问究竟。唉！赵穆真蠢，以己算人，行错这步棋，王兄对他仅余的一点顾念都不翼而飞，否则王兄仍会把事情拖着。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "大王为何不立即把赵穆抓起来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你知不知道乐乘是在怎样的情况下被杀的，二百多人，在不足半盏热茶的时间内非死即伤，赵穆的手下还未有这种本事，所以定是有人在背后给他撑腰。而且没有真凭实据，仍不可轻举妄动。王兄虽很想把廉颇或李牧召回来，但这却正中行凶者的奸计。唉！我也在为王兄为难呢！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "看来明天我还是到牧场去，可以远离是非之地，以后专心养马，空闲时抱抱女人，快快乐乐过这一生算了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那人家怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你还你，我还我，夫人的事与鄙人何干？什么知无不言，言无不尽，就像老天爷开恩般漏他娘的一句半句来，我才不稀罕呢！若非念在给你挨挨碰碰时亦颇舒服，早把你轰出去了，还来问董某什么人家怎办？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你完成承诺了吗？只懂怨人家，唉！和你一起光阴过得真快，只恨我还要入宫见王兄，待会儿人家来陪你好吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你若想我身上大小七处伤口迸裂流血，尽管来找我吧！这叫舍血陪玉人。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你总有借口拒绝人家，赵雅很惹你厌吗？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "不信你查验一下，顺便看看董某的真正本钱。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你这人呢！没有半点羞耻之心，不和你瞎缠了，送人家到门外好吗？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "夫人今夜为何兴致特高？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙走后，人家曾多次想过寻死，但却觉得太便宜赵穆了，且也想为少龙多做点事，现在成功在望，你说人家应否开怀？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "若赵穆死了，你又怎样呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "本来还不知道，现在却晓得自己终找到取代项少龙的人，其他人都不行，这么说董大人明白吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "她们呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "谁知你是否舍得回来，我把她们赶入房睡觉。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "我又不像大姊般睡足一整天，为何不顺便赶我去睡觉呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "你的脚长在我身上吗？自己不懂回房，怪得谁来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "刚才我说要去睡觉，是谁拉着我来看地图的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "快滚！现在有人陪我了。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "给我看你画了些什么鬼东西出来？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你再说一遍！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "好姊姊！请给鄙人欣赏一下你呕心沥血的杰作，好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "呕心沥血？你这人最懂夸大其辞。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "今晚陪我睡觉吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我现在没有半丝睡意，你自己回房睡个饱吧！致致在我房里，倘若欢喜就把我这个将你看得比老天爷还大的妹子抱走好了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "你睡不睡悉随尊便！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "喂！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "善小姐有何指教？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你究竟肯不肯助我们姊妹对付田单？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "来！到我的睡榻上好好商量。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "去便去吧！若你只是骗人家，我便一刀子干掉你。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "不是说好了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不！不成！",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "你又不是未和我在榻上厮混过，有什么不成的呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不！我知道今趟是不同的。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "原来凶霸如虎的柔姊，竟也有害怕得羞答答的动人时刻！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你让不让路？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "你欢喜就动刀子吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "啊！饶过我好吗？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "是否仍很痛呢？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然痛！你……噢！项少龙！你在欺负人家。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙啊！不能这样的！你连门都未关好呢！",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "我还以为大姊你天不怕、地不怕，原来竟怕一道没有关上的房门，我便顺你意思吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "柔柔你忘了带匕首。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "即使有刀在手又如何呢？区区一把匕首，可以阻止你这色鬼吗？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "你不但是一流的刺客，还是一流的天生尤物。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你放肆够了吗？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "柔姊又够了吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "停一停好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "又怎样哩？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人家早说过你今晚要图谋不轨，你看现在弄得人家成什么样子？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "什么样子？当然是最诱人可爱的样子哪！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "让人家再说几句话好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "这时候还有什么好说的？你应知接着会发生什么事。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "正因知道，所以想和你这大坏蛋作个商量。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "两军交战，一方败北，除屈服投诚外，还有什么可以商量的？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "谁要投降，你只是小战得利，人家……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "噢！我差点忘记你仍有土地没有被占领，京城尚未失守。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要过来，否则我立即溜到房外去。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "夫人乖乖地给我过来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "除非你答应不再侵犯人家。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "在这时代有哪一场仗是刚尝甜头，会忽然退兵呢？善柔你已长大成人，应知今晚有些事是无可避免的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你该心知肚明，从人家要扮你的夫人开始，善柔便拿定主意从你。但你也要体谅人家嘛！我一向看不起男人的自高自大，最不服气是像我们女儿家天生出来便是供他们淫辱欺压，动辄施虐，唉！我不懂再说了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "我会尊重柔柔的想法，今晚到此为止，你睡在我这里，我自己找地方睡觉好了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你要找致致还是田家姊妹？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "我不想弄醒她们，不是还有间空房子？我到那里去好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "想不到世上有你这种男人，处处为别人设想，好吧！我们一起到那里去好了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "一起去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "待会儿你对人家作恶完毕，立即给本姑娘滚回这里睡觉。事后绝不准对任何人提起，更休想我会像致致般对你千依百顺，若不是我主动就你，否则再不能随便对我无礼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "这是否叫掩耳盗铃呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么是掩耳盗铃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "偷铃的贼，自己掩上耳朵，听不到逃走时铃摇的声音，便以为别人也听不见，不正像小姐现在的行径吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那怎么相同？这里并没有供人掩耳的铃声！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "柔姑娘似乎忘掉自己懂得呻吟呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "来！快天亮哩！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "柔柔你忘了榻上地下，都有你盗铃的衣衫物证。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 454
    }
